data.text:
i do not get higher than version 150.

Also will the Windows installer work on Windows 8.1 x64?

I get a not working good message because a problem and the application must shutdown when try to startup the EXE file.

@anonymoustly said in When comes Ubuntu Touch 20.04 to the BQ Aquaris E4.5 Ubuntu Edition?:

will the Windows installer work on Windows 8.1 x64?

You will probably have better results if you boot the machine from a USB stick containing Ubuntu or Linux Mint, and install the UBports installer on that.
